OL,4,CGovernment will be 'forced to rely' on
OL,5,CBBC licence fee model, MPs suggest
OL,6, The government will be forced to rely
OL,7, on the current BBC TV licence fee model
OL,8, until 2038, a group of MPs has said.
OL,10,FA report from a Commons select
OL,11,Fcommittee suggests the failure to find
OL,12,Fa viable alternative form of funding
OL,13,Fmeant the licence fee must remain for
OL,14,Fthe term of the next charter.
OL,16,FA government spokeswoman said the
OL,17,Flicence fee would be reviewed before
OL,18,Fthe current charter ends in 2027.
OL,20,FThe BBC said it "welcomed this thorough
OL,21,Fand detailed report".
